data.description: Four bedroom, two bath bi-level in Lagrange awaits it's new owner!  Put your finishing touches on this great home in the heart of Lagrange. Two bedrooms, a full bath, kitchen and living room upstairs and two bedrooms, full bath, laundry room and family room on entry level. Plenty of storage, attached garage and deck off of kitchen in back! Located near shopping and restaurants. Come see this great home before its gone!
